Package org.odata4j.consumer

The odata4j client-side (consumer-side) API.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ODataClient ODataClient is one abstraction layer below ODataConsumer.
ODataClientResponse Generic OData http response used by the low-level ODataClient api.
ODataConsumer ODataConsumer is the client-side interface to an OData service.
ODataConsumer.Builder Mutable builder for ODataConsumer instances.
 

Class Summary
AbstractConsumerEntityPayloadRequest Shared consumer request implementation for operations with an entity as the request payload.
AbstractConsumerEntityRequest<T> Shared consumer request implementation for operations dealing with a single response entity.
AbstractConsumerQueryRequestBase<T> Shared consumer request implementation for operations dealing with multiple response entities.
AbstractODataClient Useful base class for ODataClient implementations with common functionality.
AbstractODataConsumer Useful base class for ODataConsumer implementations with common functionality.
ConsumerCountRequest Count-request implementation.
ConsumerCreateEntityRequest<T> Create-request implementation.
ConsumerCreateLinkRequest Create-link-request implementation.
ConsumerDeleteEntityRequest Delete-request implementation.
ConsumerDeleteLinkRequest Delete-link-request implementation.
ConsumerEntityModificationRequest<T> Modification-request implementation.
ConsumerFunctionCallRequest<T extends OObject> Function-call-request implementation.
ConsumerGetEntityRequest<T> Get-entity-request implementation.
ConsumerQueryEntitiesRequest<T> Query-request implementation.
ConsumerQueryLinksRequest Query-links-request implementation.
ConsumerUpdateLinkRequest Update-link-request implementation.
ODataClientRequest Generic OData http request builder used by the low-level ODataClient api.
ODataConsumers ODataConsumer is the client-side interface to an OData service.
ODataConsumers.Builder Builder for ODataConsumer objects.
 

Enum Summary
ODataConsumer.Dump Sends http request and/or response information to standard out.
 

Package org.odata4j.consumer Description

The odata4j client-side (consumer-side) API.

Use ODataConsumers to connect to an existing OData service.
